    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, reboil half a kettle and trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>trimmed green beans</strong> to a separate pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them!)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 2-3 min or until tender</p><p>Once tender,<strong> </strong>add your<strong> blanched peas</strong> and cook for 1 min further or until warmed through</p><p>Drain the veg and set aside for serving</p>",
