    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the veg is cooking, chop your <strong>parsley & chives</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Return the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a splash of <strong>milk</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mash together until smooth, then stir through the<strong> chopped parsley & chives</strong> – this is your<strong> herby mash</strong></p>",
