      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken & chorizo pie filling</strong> with the <strong>herby mash</strong> and <strong>green beans & peas</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the filling with a <strong>pie lid</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
